<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="8" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="9.[192,1440,1731,1883]" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,335,1731,1755]" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Galileo &amp; Martins, 2010" authorityName="Galileo &amp; Martins" authorityYear="2010" box="[340,622,1731,1755]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Cosmisoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridescens" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[340,622,1731,1755]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Cosmisoma viridescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[627,719,1732,1755]" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
could be compared with 
<taxonomicName authority="Monne and Magno, 1988" authorityName="Monne and Magno" authorityYear="1988" box="[1015,1440,1731,1756]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Cosmisoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gratum">
<emphasis box="[1015,1138,1732,1755]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">C. gratum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Monne, M. A. &amp; P. R. Magno" box="[1143,1440,1731,1756]" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" pagination="1 - 27" refId="ref5134" refString="Monne, M. A., and P. R. Magno. 1988. Genero Cosmisoma Audinet-Serville, 1834: notas, novos taxa e chave para especies sul-americanas (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae, Rhopalophorini). Boletim do Museu Nacional 319: 1 - 27." type="journal article" year="1988">Monné and Magno, 1988</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
by antennomere V, with small hair tuft on the apex; prothorax reddish; antennae and legs black, with discrete metallic-blue reflexes; elytra unicolored with metallic-green gloss and the metatibiae with hair tufts. It is distinguished by its black head and reddish-orange pronotum with a metallic-green band along the margins. The head and prothorax of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Monne and Magno" authorityYear="1988" box="[687,810,1860,1883]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Cosmisoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gratum">
<emphasis box="[687,810,1860,1883]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">C. gratum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are completely reddish.
</paragraph>
